Soundwave immidiatly transformed, leaping into the air, and shrinking
into his Cassette Deck mode. Spasstik leapt to the air, catching him in
his jaw, then began dashing towards Streetwise, leaping on top of the
police car, then using him as a platform to leap over to Rumble, and
Groove, attempting to land on Groove.
